<!-- FINAL-2-LCP 2026-05-10: Unsplash hero photo origin hints. The product
     hero <picture> below the fold may resolve runtime URLs back to Unsplash
     if the image-source-set <source> falls through; pre-warming the TCP/TLS
     handshake here saves ~150-300ms on first byte if/when that happens. -->
<link rel="dns-prefetch" href="https://images.unsplash.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://images.unsplash.com" crossorigin>
