        <span class="hp-framework-cite sv-text-tertiary">SI 2002/1674 &middot; BoE base + 8%</span>
        <p class="hp-framework-desc sv-text-secondary">Statutory interest auto-calculated to the penny + tiered statutory compensation per overdue invoice.</p>
        <a class="hp-framework-link" href="/crowcash" aria-label="Learn more about CrowCash's Late Payment coverage">Explore CrowCash <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
      </li>
      <li class="hp-framework-row" data-product="mark">
        <span class="hp-framework-mark">PPN 002 social value</span>
        <span class="hp-framework-cite sv-text-tertiary">Cabinet Office &middot; 10% bid floor</span>
