<!-- ── WHY THIS WORK MATTERS ── -->
<hr class="section-divider">
<section class="reveal sf17-reveal section-padding section-alt section-tone-0" aria-label="Why this work matters">
  <div class="wrap container-standard">
    <div class="sh">
      <div class="sh-label">Why this work matters</div>
      <h2>The regulatory pressure UK organisations face today</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="u-grid-3">
      <div class="sv-card">
        <div class="counter u-stat-number stat-teal" data-target="25" data-prefix="" data-suffix="%">25%</div>
        <div class="u-stat-title">UK emissions from the built environment</div>
        <p>The built environment accounts for approximately a quarter of UK greenhouse gas emissions. MEES, building regulations, and net zero targets all drive the same outcome: commercial landlords need to act on energy performance.</p>
        <div class="u-source-label">Source: UK Green Building Council, Net Zero Whole Life Carbon Roadmap</div>
      </div>
      <div class="sv-card">
        <div class="counter u-stat-number stat-lime" data-target="170" data-prefix="£" data-suffix="B+">£170B+</div>
        <div class="u-stat-title">Annual UK public sector procurement spend</div>
        <p>PPN 002 requires a minimum 10% social value weighting on all central government contracts. Local authorities and NHS trusts increasingly apply the same standard, putting pressure on every supplier bidding for public work.</p>
        <div class="u-source-label">Source: HM Treasury, Public Spending Statistics, July 2025 (gross current procurement 2024-25 = £170.9bn)</div>
      </div>
      <div class="sv-card">
        <div class="counter u-stat-number stat-sky" data-target="50000" data-prefix="" data-suffix="+">50,000+</div>
        <div class="u-stat-title">EU companies reassessing CSRD scope</div>
        <p>Omnibus I raised the thresholds to over 1,000 employees and more than &euro;450M in turnover. Thousands of groups that expected to report now need to confirm whether they remain in scope or fall below the new line.</p>
        <div class="u-source-label">Source: European Commission, COM(2025) 80 final - Omnibus simplification package</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

