<!-- H3-HERO-VIDEO 10-10 (2026-05-10): gate the ambient hero video on
     prefers-reduced-motion + navigator.connection.saveData. When either
     signal is present we strip the autoplay attribute, pause the element,
     and hide it so the static .hero-glow / poster fallback renders alone.
     Inlined so it executes before the decoder has a chance to spin up;
     calling .pause() in the same microtask as removeAttribute('autoplay')
     is sufficient even on browsers that begin buffering at autoplay parse. -->
